{"tid":1626260,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"點揀 VPN","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T13:49:58.000Z","uid":76701,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a2acfd6141c4b2d83279cb03accca5700bd308","tid":1626260,"uid":76701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:25:00.000Z","msg":"Sources:<br />\n1. <a href=\"http://Privacytools.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FPrivacytools.io&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=19743d36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Privacytools.io</a> - VPN : <a href=\"https://www.privacytools.io/providers/vpn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.privacytools.io%2Fproviders%2Fvpn%2F&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=0eacb44d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.privacytools.io/providers/vpn/</a><br />\n2. EFF - Surveillance self-defense: Choosing the VPN That's Right for You - <a href=\"https://ssd.eff.org/en/module/choosing-vpn-thats-right-you\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fssd.eff.org%2Fen%2Fmodule%2Fchoosing-vpn-thats-right-you&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=03a59145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ssd.eff.org/en/module/choosing-vpn-thats-right-you</a><br />\n3. <a href=\"http://Privacytools.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FPrivacytools.io&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=19743d36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Privacytools.io</a> - WebRTC IP Leak : <a href=\"https://www.privacytools.io/browsers/#webrtc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.privacytools.io%2Fbrowsers%2F%23webrtc&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=5c3b4af7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.privacytools.io/browsers/#webrtc</a><br />\n4. That one privacy site - VPN comparison : <a href=\"https://thatoneprivacysite.net/#simple-vpn-comparison\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthatoneprivacysite.net%2F%23simple-vpn-comparison&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=1c8e0965\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thatoneprivacysite.net/#simple-vpn-comparison</a><br />\n<br />\n識英文就自己睇 source，以下開始係個人意見 (搬字過紙 + plagiarising)，未整得切圖所以得字，歡迎指教。<br />\n<br />\n首先簡單解釋吓，當你想上連登嘅時候:<br />\n1. 喺 browser 輸入連登嘅 url (<a href=\"http://lihkg.com\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com</a>)<br />\n2. Browser 就會幫你連去 DNS (Domain name server) 揾連登 server 嘅 IP address<br />\n3. Browser 就會用個 IP address 幫你同連登連線<br />\n<br />\n咁會有啲咩問題呢:<br />\n1. 如果 DNS 係 ISP (Internet service provider) 指定嘅，就有機會 log 咗你真實 IP address 上過嘅網，繼而有 record 同埋可以根據你上嘅網整一個關於你嘅 profile = 白色恐怖<br />\n2. ISP 係可以紀錄低你嘅 IP address 上過嘅網，當狗方問法庭拎咗搜查令，就會得到晒你上過嘅網嘅紀錄 = 白色恐怖<br />\n3. ISP 可以限制你上到嘅網 = 限制言論自由<br />\n<br />\n用咗 VPN (Virtual private network) 之後:<br />\n1. 喺 browser 輸入連登嘅 url (<a href=\"http://lihkg.com\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com</a>)<br />\n2. Browser 首先會以加密嘅形式連去 VPN 嘅 server<br />\n3. VPN 多數會有埋自家 no logging 嘅 DNS server，中間嘅連線當然係加密，咁佢就會幫你揾到連登嘅 IP address<br />\n4. 然後 browser 就會經過 VPN server，用個 IP address 幫你同連登連線<br />\n5. ISP 只會睇你同 VPN server 有加密嘅連線，而唔知你上咩網，亦都限制唔到你上咩網<br />\n6. 而對家，即係連登只會睇到喺 VPN server 有個連線，唔會知你嘅確實 IP address<br />\n<br />\n用 VPN 有咩要注意呢:<br />\n1. VPN 主要用途只係隱藏自己嘅 IP address 同埋翻牆<br />\n2. 要隱藏自己嘅 IP address 除咗用 VPN，仲一定要 disable browser 嘅 WebRTC (<a href=\"https://www.privacytools.io/browsers/#webrtc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.privacytools.io%2Fbrowsers%2F%23webrtc&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=5c3b4af7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.privacytools.io/browsers/#webrtc</a>)<br />\n3. 如果要完全隱身，首選一定係 Tor browser，不過好慢，而且對付香港狗隊未必需要住<br />\n4. 就算有 VPN 加持，你個人嘅網絡安全意識都好重要，例如強力密碼，上網一定要用 HTTPS (無 HTTPS 嘅話，你嘅連線喺 VPN server 出嚟就己經可以比人睇晒內容)，唔好亂 click 不明嘅 link 等等<br />\n5. ISP 係可以封 VPN 嘅 IP address 嘅。 Netflix 雖然唔係 ISP，不過係成功嘅例子<br />\n<br />\n揀 VPN:<br />\n0. 唔想睇嘅我個有以下推介 Mullvad &gt; IVPN &gt; NordVPN<br />\n1. 公司地點要避免澳洲、加拿大、紐西蘭、英國、美國 (Five eyes)，因為呢幾個國家嘅監控都好嚴重，中資嘅都係一樣。詳情見: <a href=\"https://www.giswatch.org/en/communications-surveillance/unmasking-five-eyes-global-surveillance-practices\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.giswatch.org%2Fen%2Fcommunications-surveillance%2Funmasking-five-eyes-global-surveillance-practices&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=18911de9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.giswatch.org/en/communications-surveillance/unmasking-five-eyes-global-surveillance-practices</a><br />\n2. 間 VPN 喺香港有無 Server (我介紹嘅三間都有)<br />\n3. 有無經過第三方嘅 audit (Mullvad 有)<br />\n4. VPN connection protocol 我建議用 wireguard。因為 wireguard 嘅 code 簡潔，用落順，少 disconnection，attack surface 細，最新 iOS 嘅 wireguard app 己經有 on demand activation， 效果接近 kill switch 。詳見: <a href=\"https://mullvad.net/en/help/why-wireguard/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmullvad.net%2Fen%2Fhelp%2Fwhy-wireguard%2F&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=17c9a3cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mullvad.net/en/help/why-wireguard/</a> 。<br />\n唔鍾意 wireguard ，最低限度都要 OpenVPN，呢個 protocol 都用咗好多年，夠穩定同安全。其他嘅都唔建議。我推介嘅 Mullvad 同 IVPN 都有晒兩個 protocol 比你揀，而 nordvpn 個 app 就 default 係用 openvpn。<br />\n5. 有無手機 app 同電腦 app。有就當然方便啦，不過 wireguard 同 openvpn 都有自家嘅手機 app，所以就算間 VPN 公司無，都唔緊要嘅。而電腦嘅話，無 app 都唔難 setup 嘅。(Mullvad 無手機 app，IVPN 同 NordVPN 都有)<br />\n6. 儘量減少 VPN 公司拎到嘅資料，例如名、地址、信用卡號碼等等。Mullvad 唔洗開 account，佢會 generate 一個 account code，只要個 account 有錢就用到佢嘅 service，基本上係唔需要比任何個資料佢，而比錢嘅方法就有信用卡以至 Bitcoin 都得。IVPN 同 NordVPN 都要開 account，不過香港狗隊都應該無辦查到呢兩間公司，理論上可以放心。<br />\n7. 加密技術方面基本上都唔洗擔心，正常用 wireguard 同 openvpn 都無咩可能比狗隊解到密。<br />\n8. No logging policy 係必須，就算間公司收到法庭嘅搜查令，都查唔到任何嘢<br />\n9. 最後就係你對間公司嘅道德嘅信任程度，你覺得佢會唔會偷偷咁 log 低你嘅 traffic，佢受到執法機關查嘅時候會唔會屈服，佢有無 false claim 自己嘅服務係 100% 安全等等<br />\n<br />\n如果你想自己揾 VPN，或者見到抵嘅 VPN，我強烈建議你用呢個網比較吓先: <a href=\"https://thatoneprivacysite.net/#simple-vpn-comparison\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthatoneprivacysite.net%2F%23simple-vpn-comparison&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=1c8e0965\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thatoneprivacysite.net/#simple-vpn-comparison</a><br />\n<br />\n額外資料:<br />\n1. 以下幾個國家都有法例要公司喺刑事案件中交出解密鑰匙: 安提瓜和巴布達、澳洲、加拿大、法國、印度、愛爾蘭、挪威、俄羅斯、南非、英國<br />\n2. Warrant Canary 係啲 VPN 公司會每個月都 post 一次嘅聲明，話自己無收過搜查令，亦都無交出過任何資料，如果當有一個月佢無 post，就代表佢己經收咗皮。例子有: <a href=\"https://www.ivpn.net/resources/canary.txt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ivpn.net%2Fresources%2Fcanary.txt&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=a7219cd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ivpn.net/resources/canary.txt</a><br />\n3. 記住無一樣嘢係萬能，最緊要係個用家，即係你，點用個工具。Knowledge is power<br />\n4. 有機會再寫 Mullvad 新手教學，暫時自己睇 FAQ <a href=\"https://mullvad.net/en/help/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmullvad.net%2Fen%2Fhelp%2F&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=25e610ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mullvad.net/en/help/</a><br />\n5. 以下開放發問"},{"pid":"12016d4ed05d04c17f75223a8b53afee8b6af752","tid":1626260,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:35:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Surfshark VPN AC 開心些牙 (已課金)</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkG4nBJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkG4nBJ.png&h=15e46738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請各位自律，<br />\n唔好亂改密碼，<br />\nthx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>溫馨提示：無論你用緊電腦定電話版APP，<br />\n都一定一定要開 kill switch 至好連 VPN！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nWindows:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BG4v5Ei.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBG4v5Ei.png&h=9cc93906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niOS:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JwgWYkH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwgWYkH.png&h=102acdf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">極不專業 VPN 速度測試 (WIFI)</span></strong><br />\nSurfshark VPN Server: 日本 M247<br />\nSpeedtest Server: QTS HK<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vc3s7SX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvc3s7SX.png&h=caf32e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936f97791ee8da7fe300621746f71e391f0c8993","tid":1626260,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:36:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Cloudflare WARP 不能隱藏你真 IP 地址　用家身份零保護</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/10/03/warpvpncaution/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F10%2F03%2Fwarpvpncaution%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=9ba30bc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/10/03/warpvpncaution/tech-secure/</a><br />\n<br />\nWARP 自稱自己在定義上是一個「VPN」服務，但很多人預期 VPN 所提供的功能，例如<span style=\"color: red;\">最重要的隱身功能，如隱藏 IP 功能，WARP 就未能好好提供</span>，用戶要特別留意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Cloudflare WARP 不會對目標服務隱藏使用者的IP</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191004/60118170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191004%2F60118170&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=e0f54d85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191004%2F60118170&h=f5c59203\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191004/60118170</a><br />\n<br />\n有評測指出，WARP用的技術和傳統VPN不同，不會對目標服務隱藏使用者的IP，<span style=\"color: red;\">換句話說有可能不能突破地區限制的內容</span>，封網一樣死。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果記者用3個IP檢查網址做測試，包括：<a href=\"https://checkip.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcheckip.org&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=a1e16df7\" target=\"_blank\">https://checkip.org</a>、<a href=\"https://whatismyipaddress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwhatismyipaddress.com&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=33d60d2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://whatismyipaddress.com</a>、<a href=\"https://nordvpn.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnordvpn.com&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=3861ef8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://nordvpn.com</a>。<span style=\"color: red;\">發覺WARP在後2個網址中出現了原本屬於香港的124字頭IP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span>"},{"pid":"9d032be8b387f3cf43c1d5ebb69ca24b03f77430","tid":1626260,"uid":76701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12016d4ed05d04c17f75223a8b53afee8b6af752","tid":1626260,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:35:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Surfshark VPN AC 開心些牙 (已課金)</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkG4nBJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkG4nBJ.png&h=15e46738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請各位自律，<br />\n唔好亂改密碼，<br />\nthx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>溫馨提示：無論你用緊電腦定電話版APP，<br />\n都一定一定要開 kill switch 至好連 VPN！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nWindows:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BG4v5Ei.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBG4v5Ei.png&h=9cc93906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niOS:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JwgWYkH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwgWYkH.png&h=102acdf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">極不專業 VPN 速度測試 (WIFI)</span></strong><br />\nSurfshark VPN Server: 日本 M247<br />\nSpeedtest Server: QTS HK<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vc3s7SX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvc3s7SX.png&h=caf32e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正，多謝 ching"},{"pid":"0a24ba66c912995e4e731a09bc2a2712d53943bc","tid":1626260,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:51:59.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"deae09295917dbd441fc8e04422ef8349e12972a","tid":1626260,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:18:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b678a1365dc09df25fe06a3ae3aaa3da25333496","tid":1626260,"uid":17444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1bf9a8d3a245be79b8e6d277c6560ec8411075","tid":1626260,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:49:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}